title: Bandiramer gonotontro/Democracy of Bandiram
description: Bandiramer gonotontro/Democracy of Bandiram is a Bengali documentary on state repression in Indian state of West Bengal during late 90's. west Bengal in late 90's saw the reemergence of Naxalite Movement in districts like Purulia, Bankura and Medinipur and in awake of this, State Police along with central forces launched a brutal campaign against poor people of these land.
